data.description: Cool people own cool homes, now welcome to 2495 Chestnut st. The hard work has already been taken care of, allowing you to fully enjoy time with your friends and family. With 28 solar panels, you'll stay comfortable during these Savage summers, the AC unit has been meticulously serviced every year, ensuring optimal performance. Trust me, it fires right up! The spacious yard is perfect for hosting memorable events, ranging from intimate weddings to surprise birthday parties and lively New Year's Eve mixers. In this family-oriented neighborhood, you'll find the ideal space to grow your family. And why not be the friend with the pool? Contrary to popular belief, it doesn't have to break the bank. You deserve to live your best life! Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this amazing property at 2495 Chestnut St. It's more than just a house, it's a place where dreams are made and of!
